    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping it in pristine, mint condition, and it drives like a total dream. Spotless interior, glowing paint, and it's been babied since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new without that dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 48500.0,
