    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh luster on its Deep Sea Metallic finish. The exterior is free from even the slightest stone chips or swirl marks, having been treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of compression or wear, and the original protective films are still present on several interior trim pieces. Mechanically, this car is indistinguishable from new. It boasts a comprehensive, single-owner service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. Every button, sensor, and mechanical component functions with precision. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
